  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just ?] [? how-- ?] somehow differently.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The capital flew a little flag [? for to-- ?] all day long in my honor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the flag was then given to me [? to have ?] it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have a certificate from the-- I think it was a architect of the-- of the capital [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I have been honored by the Jewish-- Jewish community of Philadelphia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I got a [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Jabotinsky ?] Order.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm looking at them, what I have there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew him well, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew him-- I knew him before I started to organize the illegal transport-- the free transports.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew him before that because I was actually when I was one of the leaders of the Austrian Revisionist Movement, and he was the leader for the whole world.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew him from the congresses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I worked in Romania, his-- his sister's had-- his sister's apartment-- her name was Epstein; she was married to a Romanian Jewish surgeon-- was our headquarters.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where we [? were ?] [? back ?] from, from Mrs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Epstein's headquarters.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- he came to visit her once, twice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Once was a more personal visit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And once he-- he me with the king there, though I had more contact with him than there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had contact with him when I went from Vienna through to London.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Begin-- I knew Begin very fleetingly only.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a young [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Betarine ?] leader, and I was a [? man ?] in the [INAUDIBLE] movement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew him from there, from the meeting in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, he came once with a troop of-- with a group of [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Betarines ?] and others.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had organized an illegal transport to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
